CalculatedMember.formula: avg(PeriodsToDate([Date].[(All)], [Date].CurrentMember),[Measures].[No of All Renew])

CalculatedMember.name: No of New Member AVG AllTD Previous Year
CalculatedMember.formula: sum(parallelperiod([Date].[Year],1,[Date].CurrentMember),[Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD])

CalculatedMember.name: No of New Member AVG AllTD DIFF Previous Year
CalculatedMember.formula: [Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD] - [Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD Previous Year]

CalculatedMember.name: No of New Member AVG AllTD % DIFF Previous Year
CalculatedMember.caption: ค่าเฉลี่ย % สมาชิกใหม่เทียบกับปีที่แล้ว [5]
CalculatedMember.formula: IIF([Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD Previous Year]=0,null,[Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD DIFF Previous Year] / [Measures].[No of New Member AVG AllTD Previous Year])

CalculatedMember.name: Sum of Point
